  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is the registry of control participants for patients with various respiratory diseases.
      We screened healthy volunteers who visited Seoul National Hospital Healthcare System Gangnam
      Center for routine health check-up, and enrolled patients who agree to participate in the
      study. The participants undergo baseline questionnaires, provide blood specimen and
      information of the results of health check-up. We will include participants as controls if
      they have no significant respiratory symptom and no significant radiographic abnormality. The
      data from this registry will be compared with those from other registry of various
      respiratory diseases
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
